{"tid":2097484,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"隸屬中國教育部的540間「孔子學院」，今後改由「民間組織」營運","createTime":"2020-07-07T00:59:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T08:44:56.000Z","uid":48040,"like":4,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"b36d59cd02170f97758a0b8c0ed62d87070f2488","tid":2097484,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T00:59:47.000Z","msg":"根據官方數據，中國目前在全球162個國家和地區共有540所孔子學院，以及在中小學運作的1154個孔子課堂。<br />\n<br />\n但是，隨著近年在國際間引發爭議，被不少外國大學關閉的孔子學院，近期有了一次重大的&ldquo;改革&rdquo;。原本由中國國家漢語國際推廣領導小組辦公室（簡稱漢辦）統轄的孔子學院，現在改由&ldquo;中國國際中文教育基金會&rdquo;負責。<br />\n<br />\n按照中國官方的說法，這一中文教育基金會是由多家高校和企業發起成立的&ldquo;民間公益組織&rdquo;，將&ldquo;全面負責運行全球孔子學院品牌&rdquo;。如此一來，原本隸屬中國教育部的&ldquo;孔子學院&rdquo;，被改變成為民間公益組織運營，<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-53308869\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-53308869&d=uYDAXyhVPN7xTSuHIXBXEtHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=cdd2a74b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-53308869&h=4fba5ea5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-53308869</a><br />\n<br />\n======<br />\n黃channel撐得好辛苦，可以幫手subscribe嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TyuR4gnpUqs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTyuR4gnpUqs&d=uYDAXyhVPN7xTSuHIXBXEtHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=a66335b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TyuR4gnpUqs</a>"},{"pid":"e94e74eab61b8520920998964e0b64e4cbf78a00","tid":2097484,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T01:00:34.000Z","msg":"人唔吠"},{"pid":"9cd96720088ee2766ef325cea15587528da1b158","tid":2097484,"uid":116289,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T01:00:55.000Z","msg":"換層皮扮民間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa80